method.\n\n5. **java.security** (src/java.base/share/conf/security/java.security): The master security properties file that statically configures providers using security.provider.<n>=<providerName> entries. Line 100 lists SunJCE as a registered provider, and the file documents the provider registration mechanism and preference order (line 74-75).\n\nThe call chain flows: Cipher.getInstance() → Security.getProvider() or provider.getService() → Provider.Service → implementation class instantiation via reflection."
